## 0 · Architectural principles inherited

- **P1 Portability** — runtime LLM-agnostic (Tier A).
- **P2 Calibration** — every architectural claim quantified.
- **P3 On-demand** — no component "just in case".
- **P4 prompt-architect** — every prompt audited.
- **P5 Living docs** — `tracking/` + `memory/` + `audit/` updated continuously.

